{"tid":81522,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"陳淨心瘋狂狙擊 一個月開7帖鬧爆張敬軒係反骨仔","createTime":"2017-01-15T11:30:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-15T14:37:09.000Z","uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f3dccfd711c13cd0d5394efe8abdb820360e191e","tid":81522,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T11:30:25.000Z","msg":"「愛港力」代表人物陳淨心曾經喺微博狙擊張敬軒參加湖南衛視《我是歌手4》，指軒仔出力反國民教育兼支持佔中，傳軒仔前年被退出比賽，但當時英皇高層霍汶希指公司曾探討軒仔參賽事宜，仍未決定，所以唔存在退出問題。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170115/large/1484471408_7701.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170115%2Flarge%2F1484471408_7701.jpg&h=df7a82b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一年過去，軒仔終於成功入閘，參加新一季《我是歌手5》（現改名《歌手》），並已錄影第一集；但昨日突然有內地網民爆料軒仔再一次被踢出局，連英皇廣州總經理周峰剛剛都喺微博留言暗示﹕「沒有難過，只有憤怒！」<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170115/large/1484457875_582d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170115%2Flarge%2F1484457875_582d.jpg&h=a5942fa0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實睇番陳淨心最近嘅微博又確實出咗唔少力，去年底開始，軒仔未正式宣佈參與《歌手》時，淨心BB已經開post不停鬧爆軒仔，未夠一個月已先後開咗7個post，其中一個鬧﹕「廣州人張敬軒是反骨仔，忘恩負義！拿了香港身份搞亂香港，煽動兩地分化矛盾，如果你能回內地賺人民幣，簡直天理難容！不愛國家不愛民族只愛人民幣是不可能的！國家面前無偶像！」<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170115/large/1484470451_a779.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170115%2Flarge%2F1484470451_a779.jpg&h=55ab16be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過都有好多軒仔嘅fans留言反擊陳淨心，搞到陳淨心都忍唔住要爆seed：「向祖國感恩有問題嗎？張敬軒的言論都在諷刺蔣麗雲議員的，難道張敬軒你可以選擇喝英國水長大的嗎？粉絲不用天天為你偶像洗地了。」"},{"pid":"4434896c223102952ab7a77aa5876c19be093e77","tid":81522,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T11:46:57.000Z","msg":"啲圖咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"146bb80b9fa5623c98df4ddb95a3f47448cf9421","tid":81522,"uid":22869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T11:51:03.000Z","msg":"Where is Tracy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76969cc7273f048f4b9aad79996a06cbb3ece0a6","tid":81522,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T11:54:59.000Z","msg":"第一張:反骨仔"},{"pid":"33ad6a532481d1fa9a15e95828fc784444581e33","tid":81522,"uid":37524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T13:56:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲圖咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有暗示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3625fd45eed3d6a4b24df5d8874f7a60b35e08d","tid":81522,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T14:37:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>啲圖咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有暗示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n特色黎，唔洗理"}]}